            Since joining the company, customer enrollment in autopay has grown from 1,000 to 350,000+ in the period of three years.
            When I originally joined, we could barely support 5,000 autopayments a day;
            now, we are able to handle 500,000+ in a timely manner largely due to my efforts.
            In other words, the core part of my job is to handle payments enmasse.
            Furthermore, I modernize the look and feel of our systems;
            <a href="https://www.expresslanedefensivedriving.com">ExpressLane Defensive Driving</a>
            is a production example of a redesign I did shortly after joining Tyler Tech.
        </p>
